text: Lenka Honzáková, married surname Popkin (born April 16, 1978) is a Czech Olympic trampoline gymnast. She competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics. She is married to American trampolinist David Popkin.Musím pryč od trampolíny, říká Češka Lenka Honzáková-Popkin at iDNES.cz, 18 August 2008. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Gymnasts at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Czech female trampolinists Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Czech Republic
